data.description: BUYER OFFERING $5,000 USE AS YOU CHOOSE! Discover this spectacular 3-bedroom home nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac street in the charming Marsh Haven community of Sneads Ferry, North Carolina. This meticulously maintained gem offers 3 bedrooms with a bonus room and 2.5 bathrooms, including a luxurious ensuite master bath. The kitchen boasts beautiful granite countertops, modern appliances, and ample cabinet space. Marsh Haven amenities include a playground, fishing spots, green spaces, waterfront walking trails, and a kayak launch. Nearby military installations like Stone Bay and Camp Lejeune Gate make it an excellent choice for those serving in our armed forces. Topsail Beach is just minutes away, allowing you to enjoy the coastal lifestyle with ease. Dixon Elementary, Middle, and High Schools are all conveniently close. Sneads Ferry, a charming fishing town, offers a strong sense of community and it's all within a short drive. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your forever home. Your coastal dream awaits in Sneads Ferry, North Carolina!
